name: Force Push (V)
Lore: 'A fully-trained Sith warrior has more weapons at his disposal than just a lightsaber.',
Text: 'Once per game, choose: during battle, use 2 Force to target your Dark Jedi and opponent''s character of equal or lesser ability present. Both targets are excluded from battle. OR Exchange two cards from hand with any one card from Force Pile; reshuffle.',
